                        p.details-container__text Keep your employees informed about changing requirements for domestic and international travel, without the tedious research.


        article.return-to-work-container
            h2.return-to-work-container__title Return-to-work safely
            p.return-to-work-container__subtitle Know employees have taken the proper health and safety precautions to return to in-person work.
            .return-to-work-container__content
                .return-to-work-container__left
                   img.return-to-work-container__img-1(src=require("../../images/employers/return-to-work1.png") alt='Return')
