            .inner
                .future-proof__main-text
                    h2.future-proof__title Future Proof
                    p.future-proof__subtitle No matter how the virus mutates; new booster shots arrive; CDC, federal and state guidelines change; and CEOs adjust corporate mandates — HR can be rest assured that diyaHR COVID Compliance will adapt to their needs.
